703223f.title: Brooklyn: Bergen Street - Albany Avenue
703223f.text:
Bergen Street, at the N.w. corner of Albany Ave., showing a view of
the Commercial High School.
About 1928.
Eugene L Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.

703222f-b.title: Brooklyn: Bergen Street - Albany Avenue
703222f-b.text:
Bergen Street, east from Albany Avenue. Note the old trolley barns
on the lefb.
March 29, 1932
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCEIONS
(2)
The same, at a later date. The car barns have been abandoned.
September 12, 1940 .
P. L. Sperr
